<section class="page-template" data-section-id="{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h1 class="page-template__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-light text-center" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
    <div class="page-template__content">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you visit our store, we collect certain information about your device, your interaction with the store, and the information necessary to process your purchases. We may also collect additional information if you contact us for customer support.</p>
      <p><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, billing/shipping address, payment information (processed securely via our payment providers).</p>
      <p><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, IP address, time zone, cookie information, and how you interact with the site.</p>
      <p><strong>Order Information:</strong> Products purchased, payment method, shipping details, and order history.</p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Fulfill orders and process payments</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about orders, products, and promotions</li>
        <li>Screen orders for potential risk or fraud</li>
        <li>Improve our store, products, and customer experience</li>
        <li>Provide customer support</li>
        <li>Send marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
      <p>We share your personal information with third parties only to help us operate our business:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Shopify:</strong> Our e-commerce platform that stores and processes your data</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> To securely process transactions</li>
        <li><strong>Shipping Partners:</strong> To deliver your orders</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To understand how customers use our store</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to maintain your shopping cart, remember your preferences, and understand how you use our store. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your order information for our records unless you request deletion. If you've made a purchase, we retain transaction data for accounting and tax compliance purposes.</p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at the email below.</p>

      <h2>7. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information. All payment transactions are encrypted and processed through PCI-compliant payment processors.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "last modified" date.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For questions about this privacy policy or your personal data, please contact us:</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@{{ shop.domain }}">privacy@{{ shop.domain }}</a></p>
      <p>Or use our <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}pages/contact">contact form</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Privacy Policy",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
